<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's okay. It's always like this.</font>

178
00:12:48,239 --> 00:12:49,307
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">And your girlfriend...</font>

179
00:12:49,574 --> 00:12:52,610
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">If she's going to do this,
she should have hidden it better.</font>

180
00:12:53,077 --> 00:12:54,912
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">If it were me,
I would execute it perfectly.</font>

181
00:12:54,979 --> 00:12:56,481
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Like a Mendel experiment.</font>

182
00:12:57,081 --> 00:12:58,883
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I wouldn't expect anything
like that from her.</font>

183
00:12:59,417 --> 00:13:01,886
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">She isn't even aware
of the trouble she's causing you.</font>

184
00:13:01,953 --> 00:13:03,688
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That's hard on you.</font>

185
00:13:04,122 --> 00:13:04,989
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Even so,</font>

186
00:13:06,290 --> 00:13:10,161
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">trying her best even if she's bad at it</font>

187
00:13:10,828 --> 00:13:12,930
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">is better than being great
at hiding things.</font>

188
00:13:18,202 --> 00:13:19,437
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">So, Uehara, do you know</font>

189
00:13:21,272 --> 00:13:22,640
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">why Nao started working part-time?</font>

190
00:13:24,876 --> 00:13:27,812
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-She said that she wanted something.
-It was to buy you a present.</font>

191
00:13:32,650 --> 00:13:34,152
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">She really loves you.</font>

192
00:13:36,854 --> 00:13:38,289
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You better act surprised.</font>

193
00:13:40,091 --> 00:13:42,026
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Don't let Nao's feelings go to waste.</font>

194
00:13:51,135 --> 00:13:53,004
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Are you going keep acting like that?</font>

195
00:13:57,141 --> 00:13:58,209
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What are you talking about?</font>

196
00:14:02,280 --> 00:14:04,715
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hiding your feelings toward Yoshikawa.</font>

197
00:14:08,886 --> 00:14:10,321
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You're acting strange today, Saeko.</font>

198
00:14:14,125 --> 00:14:14,959
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I...</font>

199
00:14:16,394 --> 00:14:18,029
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I think...</font>

200
00:14:20,731 --> 00:14:23,801
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I might have feelings for Uehara.</font>

201
00:14:32,109 --> 00:14:33,644
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What a relief!</font>

202
00:14:34,812 --> 00:14:38,149
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yes, it must be true.
It's clear to me now that I've said it.</font>

203
00:14:41,252 --> 00:14:42,887
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That came out of nowhere.</font>

204
00:14:43,254 --> 00:14:44,088
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What?</font>

205
00:14:44,922 --> 00:14:46,924
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But I thought that we were
in the same situation.</font>

206
00:14:48,960 --> 00:14:50,728
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I like happy relationships,</font>

207
00:14:51,195 --> 00:14:53,464
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">but I have no interest
in suffering and struggling.</font>

208
00:14:55,266 --> 00:14:58,936
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">And there is no way I would ever go
for a friend's girlfriend.</font>

209
00:15:01,105 --> 00:15:01,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Right.</font>

210
00:15:02,773 --> 00:15:05,009
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">And those two aren't going to break up.</font>

211
00:15:06,210 --> 00:15:08,145
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-You don't know that.
-I know it!</font>

212
00:15:08,946 --> 00:15:11,549
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It would be wise for you to step back
before it's too late.</font>

213
00:15:13,518 --> 00:15:16,420
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I would rather face it
and regret it later on</font>

214
00:15:16,988 --> 00:15:19,056
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">than do nothing and regret it.</font>

215
00:15:21,092 --> 00:15:22,627
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uehara said it himself.</font>

216
00:15:23,661 --> 00:15:24,795
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's better to be bad at it</font>

217
00:15:25,263 --> 00:15:27,465
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">and still do your best
than just be good at hiding things.</font>

218
00:15:28,833 --> 00:15:30,635
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Doesn't that depend
on the time and situation?</font>

219
00:15:44,882 --> 00:15:46,684
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Daichi.
-Nanase.</font>

220
00:15:47,218 --> 00:15:49,420
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">The coach says he wants to meet
with you before practice.</font>

221
00:15:49,520 --> 00:15:50,454
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">He told me to find you.</font>

222
00:15:50,555 --> 00:15:51,656
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I see. All right.</font>

223
00:15:52,290 --> 00:15:53,224
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Go on ahead.</font>

224
00:15:53,357 --> 00:15:55,493
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Okay.
-See you later. Bye.</font>

225
00:16:00,231 --> 00:16:02,066
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I put it on. What do you think?</font>

226
00:16:03,734 --> 00:16:07,038
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What do I think?
Well, I gave it to you so...</font>

227
00:16:07,104 --> 00:16:08,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Right. Of course.</font>

228
00:16:08,739 --> 00:16:10,808
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But when I told those guys
that you gave this to me,</font>

229
00:16:10,875 --> 00:16:11,876
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">they wanted their own too.</font>

230
00:16:12,343 --> 00:16:13,444
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">How come?</font>

231
00:16:13,511 --> 00:16:15,846
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Well, it makes them feel
like you're watching them,</font>

232
00:16:15,913 --> 00:16:17,548
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">so they can't skip practice. It's perfect.</font>

233
00:16:21,419 --> 00:16:22,587
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Mission accomplished!</font>

234
00:16:23,254 --> 00:16:27,425
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's instilled with my manager's spirit
saying, "You will definitely win!"</font>

235
00:16:27,758 --> 00:16:29,260
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I knew that was it.</font>

236
00:16:29,727 --> 00:16:31,262
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's a talisman.</font>

237
00:16:32,396 --> 00:16:33,965
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It doesn't have such an effect.</font>

238
00:16:34,031 --> 00:16:35,600
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's just a key holder.</font>

239
00:16:35,766 --> 00:16:36,601
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Really?</font>

240
00:16:36,734 --> 00:16:38,536
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But you put your heart into it.</font>

241
00:16:39,837 --> 00:16:41,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I should cherish it.</font>

242
00:16:44,442 --> 00:16:45,943
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Coach is waiting for me, isn't he?</font>

243
00:16:46,410 --> 00:16:47,244
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">See you!</font>

244
00:17:00,558 --> 00:17:02,093
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Good night, Uehara.</font>

245
00:17:02,326 --> 00:17:03,361
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Sure.
-Okay.</font>

246
00:17:19,410 --> 00:17:21,946
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm sorry. I will borrow this for a bit.</font>

247
00:17:27,184 --> 00:17:28,419
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">"At 9:00 p.m.</font>

248
00:17:29,153 --> 00:17:31,188
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">when Uehara is about to go home,</font>

249
00:17:31,656 --> 00:17:33,491
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">stop him with a computer magazine.</font>

250
00:17:34,558 --> 00:17:36,327
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uehara will be happy."</font>

251
00:17:39,697 --> 00:17:41,232
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>Uehara will be happy.</i></font>

252
00:17:44,635 --> 00:17:47,438
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>At 10:00 p.m., when Uehara
is about to head home,</i></font>

253
00:17:48,139 --> 00:17:50,641
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>stop him with a DVD that he likes.</i></font>

254
00:17:51,475 --> 00:17:53,611
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>While he is enjoying it,</i></font>

255
00:17:53,711 --> 00:17:56,681
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>go to his place and decorate it very fast.</i></font>

256
00:17:57,348 --> 00:17:59,784
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">European style? I don't know!</font>

257
00:18:00,985 --> 00:18:01,986
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>At 11:30 p.m.,</i></font>

258
00:18:03,054 --> 00:18:04,522
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>when Uehara goes back to his place,</i></font>

259
00:18:05,723 --> 00:18:08,559
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>he will turn on the light
and be surprised by it.</i></font>

260
00:18:10,161 --> 00:18:12,163
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>Then I will appear with a cake!</i></font>

261
00:18:13,097 --> 00:18:14,932
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>Uehara will be so surprised.</i></font>

262
00:18:15,566 --> 00:18:19,236
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>He would have thought I'd forgotten,
but I will yell, "Happy Birthday!"</i></font>

263
00:18:20,638 --> 00:18:22,373
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>I will give him the best present!</i></font>

264
00:18:22,807 --> 00:18:24,642
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>And Uehara will be so moved.</i></font>

265
00:18:26,644 --> 00:18:27,712
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hello!</font>

266
00:18:30,114 --> 00:18:31,449
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Okay. Next!</font>

267
00:18:32,550 --> 00:18:37,421
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>"Yoshikawa remembered my birthday.
I'm really happy."</i></font>

268
00:18:38,355 --> 00:18:40,357
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>"Of course I remembered, Uehara."</i></font>

269
00:18:41,025 --> 00:18:41,859
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>"Yoshikawa."</i></font>

270
00:18:42,326 --> 00:18:43,360
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>"Uehara."</i></font>

271
00:18:44,895 --> 00:18:47,198
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>And then, the two of us...</i></font>

272
00:18:49,667 --> 00:18:50,701
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uehara.</font>

273
00:18:52,770 --> 00:18:56,674
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Happy birthday.</font>

274
00:19:07,451 --> 00:19:11,756
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">ONE DAY BEFORE THE SURPRISE PARTY</font>

275
00:19:11,822 --> 00:19:12,656
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What do I do?</font>

276
00:19:21,866 --> 00:19:23,400
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Welcome home, Uehara.</font>

277
00:19:23,467 --> 00:19:24,401
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Sure.</font>

278
00:19:24,502 --> 00:19:26,370
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I hope you had a good day.</font>

279
00:19:30,975 --> 00:19:34,311
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Will I be able to act surprised tomorrow?</font>

280
00:19:46,657 --> 00:19:47,958
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Things Uehara likes</font>

281
00:19:48,025 --> 00:19:50,761
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I shouldn't have asked so many questions.</font>

282
00:19:51,328 --> 00:19:53,864
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I have so much information I can't decide.</font>

283
00:20:00,237 --> 00:20:01,138
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's okay.</font>

284
00:20:01,906 --> 00:20:04,809
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I will be able to find
a lovely present eventually.</font>

285
00:20:17,721 --> 00:20:20,758
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">UEHARA</font>

286
00:20:22,226 --> 00:20:26,597
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">THE DAY OF THE SURPRISE PARTY</font>

287
00:20:39,276 --> 00:20:40,110
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What?</font>

288
00:20:41,745 --> 00:20:42,580
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What do I do?</font>

289
00:20:45,883 --> 00:20:46,717
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What do I do?</font>

290
00:20:47,318 --> 00:20:48,619
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Act naturally...</font>

291
00:20:50,054 --> 00:20:52,323
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">In a completely casual way.</font>

292
00:20:55,192 --> 00:20:56,126
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That's not quite right.</font>

293
00:20:56,193 --> 00:20:57,027
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">One.</font>

294
00:20:57,962 --> 00:20:58,796
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Two.</font>

295
00:21:01,866 --> 00:21:02,733
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hello.</font>

296
00:21:02,800 --> 00:21:04,635
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh! Hello.</font>

297
00:21:06,303 --> 00:21:08,138
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hey!</font>

298
00:21:11,041 --> 00:21:13,577
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">If you'd like...</font>

299
00:21:13,677 --> 00:21:14,578
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hello!</font>

300
00:21:14,678 --> 00:21:16,680
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hello. Saeko!</font>

301
00:21:16,747 --> 00:21:19,917
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's about yesterday's quantitative
PCR experiment.</font>

302
00:21:20,451 --> 00:21:22,052
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Take a look at this.</font>

303
00:21:22,453 --> 00:21:24,388
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Do it again.
-What?</font>

304
00:21:24,688 --> 00:21:25,689
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Don't "what" me!</font>

305
00:21:26,056 --> 00:21:27,458
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Do it all over again!</font>

306
00:21:54,518 --> 00:21:58,689
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yes! This is it!
Black, not too showy, not too plain.</font>

307
00:21:58,756 --> 00:22:00,524
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">He can use it every day,
it's water resistant,</font>

308
00:22:00,591 --> 00:22:03,394
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">it will last for years, it looks good,
and it's smooth.</font>

309
00:22:07,097 --> 00:22:08,365
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Excuse me.</font>

310
00:22:08,432 --> 00:22:09,366
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Pardon me.</font>

311
00:22:15,205 --> 00:22:16,774
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Wait!</font>

312
00:22:16,874 --> 00:22:19,476
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I would like to buy that.</font>

313
00:22:19,944 --> 00:22:21,712
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm sorry, ma'am.</font>

314
00:22:21,779 --> 00:22:27,051
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That customer over there
has already purchased this item.</font>

315
00:22:28,585 --> 00:22:29,420
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What?</font>

316
00:22:29,720 --> 00:22:32,856
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">If you put in an order,
you can receive it in a week.</font>

317
00:23:02,453 --> 00:23:03,287
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Do you know her?</font>

318
00:23:05,489 --> 00:23:06,323
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No.</font>

319
00:23:24,608 --> 00:23:25,809
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Natsume.</font>

320
00:23:27,811 --> 00:23:28,645
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Here.</font>

321
00:23:30,614 --> 00:23:31,448
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Thank you.</font>

322
00:23:33,283 --> 00:23:34,118
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What are you doing?</font>

323
00:23:35,119 --> 00:23:36,286
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Isn't today Uehara's birthday?</font>

324
00:23:39,123 --> 00:23:40,090
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">How did you know that?</font>

325
00:23:41,158 --> 00:23:43,260
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You told me that it was the reason
you started working.</font>

326
00:23:49,099 --> 00:23:50,734
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That's true.</font>

327
00:23:54,271 --> 00:23:57,975
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But I still haven't found
the most important thing, a present.</font>

328
00:24:03,213 --> 00:24:04,048
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I see.</font>

329
00:24:05,749 --> 00:24:06,583
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yes.</font>

330
00:24:11,622 --> 00:24:13,490
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Isn't Uehara going to be home soon?</font>

331
00:24:16,226 --> 00:24:17,327
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yes.</font>

332
00:24:17,795 --> 00:24:19,797
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I planned to surprise him,</font>

333
00:24:21,331 --> 00:24:22,166
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">but...</font>

334
00:24:23,267 --> 00:24:26,537
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It can't be helped.
I think I will just have to apologize</font>

335
00:24:28,505 --> 00:24:29,973
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">and give it to him next time.</font>

336
00:24:39,149 --> 00:24:40,184
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That won't do.</font>

337
00:24:42,820 --> 00:24:43,654
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What?</font>

338
00:24:47,057 --> 00:24:49,960
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Well, but...</font>

339
00:24:50,461 --> 00:24:53,697
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I really should give him a present
that I think is right for him.</font>

340
00:24:54,164 --> 00:24:55,065
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That's not what I mean.</font>

341
00:24:56,300 --> 00:24:59,470
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">He won't be happy at all if you celebrate
his birthday with that look on your face.</font>

342
00:25:01,071 --> 00:25:01,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What?</font>

343
00:25:04,441 --> 00:25:08,245
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">A birthday is not a day
about giving presents,</font>

344
00:25:09,847 --> 00:25:11,782
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">it's about celebrating
the date of someone's birth.</font>

345
00:25:15,719 --> 00:25:18,055
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">All I'm saying is,
you shouldn't look so sad.</font>

346
00:25:27,898 --> 00:25:28,799
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Right.</font>

347
00:25:30,200 --> 00:25:31,068
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Right.</font>

348
00:25:38,775 --> 00:25:39,877
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You're right.</font>

349
00:25:42,746 --> 00:25:44,481
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's a day for wishing a happy birthday.</font>

350
00:25:45,649 --> 00:25:47,351
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I shouldn't look sad.</font>

351
00:25:50,821 --> 00:25:51,755
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Alright!</font>

352
00:25:56,093 --> 00:25:59,630
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm always getting help from you, Natsume.</font>

353
00:26:01,598 --> 00:26:02,432
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Thank you.</font>

354
00:26:13,710 --> 00:26:14,711
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">This is the last time.</font>

355
00:26:18,248 --> 00:26:19,082
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What?</font>

356
00:26:20,017 --> 00:26:21,552
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Are you Natsume's girlfriend?</font>

357
00:26:23,921 --> 00:26:26,089
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No way. So she's the type
of girl you like.</font>

358
00:26:29,993 --> 00:26:32,563
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-No, I'm...
-Of course not.</font>

359
00:26:33,630 --> 00:26:35,499
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Even I have the right to be choosy.</font>

360
00:26:38,368 --> 00:26:39,236
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What's with you?</font>

361
00:26:39,303 --> 00:26:41,538
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Well, good luck.</font>

362
00:26:49,446 --> 00:26:50,280
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It will be okay.</font>

363
00:26:51,682 --> 00:26:54,518
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Your feelings will reach Uehara, Nao.</font>

364
00:27:00,857 --> 00:27:01,692
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Let's go.</font>

365
00:27:12,502 --> 00:27:15,539
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What? I never heard about that!</font>

366
00:27:16,840 --> 00:27:18,709
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It was a last-minute decision
for us to attend.</font>

367
00:27:18,775 --> 00:27:20,143
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What am I supposed to do?</font>

368
00:27:20,210 --> 00:27:23,313
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">We don't have the tiniest thing ready
for an academic conference!</font>

369
00:27:26,216 --> 00:27:28,018
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Look who's here! Uehara!</font>

370
00:27:28,085 --> 00:27:29,586
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hey, Uehara. Are you free today?</font>

371
00:27:29,686 --> 00:27:31,888
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Professor, today is Uehara's...
-You're free? Thank you!</font>

372
00:27:32,489 --> 00:27:33,991
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Boy, you smell nice, Uehara.</font>

373
00:27:34,057 --> 00:27:36,927
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">So the three of us
will work together today,</font>

374
00:27:36,994 --> 00:27:39,596
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">and get through this crisis!</font>

375
00:27:39,696 --> 00:27:40,530
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Professor.</font>

376
00:27:42,799 --> 00:27:44,368
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Wait, professor!</font>

377
00:27:50,073 --> 00:27:50,907
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Can you stay?</font>

378
00:27:54,478 --> 00:27:56,179
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's hard to believe
you'd say such a thing.</font>

379
00:27:57,514 --> 00:28:00,017
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You never cared
about other people's plans.</font>

380
00:28:00,384 --> 00:28:03,053
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-How rude! Even I...
-I'll help you.</font>

381
00:28:04,855 --> 00:28:06,690
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I can't stay all night, though.</font>

382
00:28:17,901 --> 00:28:20,971
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's an awkward timing,
but happy birthday!</font>

383
00:28:22,306 --> 00:28:28,412
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You know Uehara,
I think you are amazingly manly!</font>

384
00:28:45,729 --> 00:28:49,933
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That wasn't casual at all.</font>

385
00:28:53,136 --> 00:28:56,273
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I have to work overtime,
I will be a bit late.</font>

386
00:29:03,547 --> 00:29:04,514
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, it's hot!</font>

387
00:29:15,058 --> 00:29:18,862
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">"I have to work overtime,
I will be a bit late."</font>

388
00:29:22,232 --> 00:29:23,767
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Roger that!</font>

389
00:29:37,647 --> 00:29:38,749
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Where should we go next?</font>

390
00:29:43,253 --> 00:29:44,121
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, gosh.</font>

391
00:29:44,221 --> 00:29:46,256
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That girl there is mine.</font>

392
00:29:47,657 --> 00:29:49,459
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What? You have a boyfriend?</font>

393
00:29:50,460 --> 00:29:51,328
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yes.</font>

394
00:29:51,428 --> 00:29:53,029
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Do you want to come with us for a minute?</font>

395
00:29:54,564 --> 00:29:55,565
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Okay.</font>

396
00:29:56,366 --> 00:29:57,434
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Don't go.</font>

397
00:29:57,701 --> 00:29:59,970
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Just ignore them like how you usually...
-It's okay.</font>

398
00:30:00,837 --> 00:30:02,706
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I feel like cutting loose anyway.</font>

399
00:30:06,143 --> 00:30:08,211
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uehara is so late.</font>

400
00:30:13,383 --> 00:30:15,318
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>Won't your girlfriend be angry?</i></font>

401
00:30:15,986 --> 00:30:18,822
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No. Actually, she would probably get angry</font>

402
00:30:19,356 --> 00:30:21,558
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">if I was busy at work
but I came home on time.</font>

403
00:30:24,161 --> 00:30:26,062
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But I'm sorry.</font>

404
00:30:26,930 --> 00:30:29,900
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I don't want to keep her waiting too long.</font>

405
00:30:32,102 --> 00:30:33,136
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Sure.</font>

406
00:30:33,970 --> 00:30:34,871
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Of course.</font>

407
00:30:37,941 --> 00:30:39,643
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I will be off then.</font>

408
00:30:41,978 --> 00:30:43,747
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">See you. Thank you.</font>

409
00:30:43,814 --> 00:30:46,183
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No, I'm sorry I couldn't help
until the end.</font>

410
00:30:46,650 --> 00:30:47,484
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's fine.</font>

411
00:30:48,485 --> 00:30:50,821
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Thank you for taking the trouble
to get me a cake.</font>

412
00:30:51,588 --> 00:30:53,089
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Not at all.</font>

413
00:30:53,356 --> 00:30:54,691
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Well, good luck.</font>

414
00:30:55,058 --> 00:30:55,892
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yes.</font>

415
00:31:26,857 --> 00:31:30,494
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">From Uehara:
I'm on my way home.</font>

416
00:31:33,096 --> 00:31:33,964
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, right.</font>

417
00:31:34,865 --> 00:31:36,166
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's time now.</font>

418
00:31:37,033 --> 00:31:37,868
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">All right.</font>

419
00:31:39,202 --> 00:31:41,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">"Don't go back to your own place.</font>

420
00:31:43,840 --> 00:31:50,180
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Come straight to my place."</font>

421
00:31:59,422 --> 00:32:01,024
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Natsume is in real trouble.</font>

422
00:32:01,691 --> 00:32:03,360
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">He's probably getting beaten up.</font>

423
00:32:06,429 --> 00:32:07,264
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I don't know.</font>

424
00:32:07,364 --> 00:32:08,198
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hey!</font>

425
00:32:27,784 --> 00:32:28,618
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nice.</font>

426
00:32:29,152 --> 00:32:29,986
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hey!</font>

427
00:32:32,722 --> 00:32:33,823
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">One more!</font>

428
00:32:39,329 --> 00:32:42,399
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">All you're good at is being flirty
and acting charming.</font>

429
00:32:42,499 --> 00:32:44,200
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">How lame!</font>

430
00:32:44,935 --> 00:32:46,803
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I was just thinking the same thing.</font>

431
00:32:48,672 --> 00:32:49,773
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Get up!</font>

432
00:32:52,075 --> 00:32:53,743
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Do you think I'm funny?</font>

433
00:32:54,844 --> 00:32:55,679
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hey!</font>

434
00:33:00,283 --> 00:33:01,117
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uehara.</font>

435
00:33:01,351 --> 00:33:02,719
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Who the hell are you?</font>

436
00:33:34,284 --> 00:33:35,452
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Could something have happened?</font>

437
00:33:40,390 --> 00:33:41,825
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You look awful.</font>

438
00:33:43,927 --> 00:33:44,894
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Why did you come for me?</font>

439
00:33:46,029 --> 00:33:47,664
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I just happened to be passing by.</font>

440
00:33:47,897 --> 00:33:50,166
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Liar. Isn't Nao waiting for you?</font>

441
00:33:50,433 --> 00:33:51,868
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yes, that's why I'm going home.</font>

442
00:33:52,535 --> 00:33:55,038
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Then forget about me and go. Now.</font>

443
00:33:56,673 --> 00:33:58,208
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-I can't.
-What?</font>

444
00:33:58,908 --> 00:34:00,243
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I won't be able to sleep well.</font>

445
00:34:02,479 --> 00:34:03,313
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Let's go.</font>

446
00:34:04,014 --> 00:34:04,848
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">"Let's go"?</font>

447
00:34:05,382 --> 00:34:06,216
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">To my place.</font>

448
00:34:07,884 --> 00:34:08,718
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'll patch you up.</font>

449
00:34:10,820 --> 00:34:11,921
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Can't I refuse?</font>

450
00:34:12,455 --> 00:34:13,289
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You can't.</font>

451
00:34:14,457 --> 00:34:15,291
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Come on.</font>

452
00:34:25,535 --> 00:34:27,270
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm really sorry.</font>

453
00:34:30,273 --> 00:34:32,042
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You owe me big time for this.</font>

454
00:34:33,576 --> 00:34:34,411
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yes.</font>

455
00:34:36,046 --> 00:34:37,881
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Treat me at the cafeteria
and then we're even.</font>

456
00:34:41,751 --> 00:34:42,585
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Okay.</font>

457
00:34:43,887 --> 00:34:45,755
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Don't forget about Nao's surprise.</font>

458
00:34:46,690 --> 00:34:49,526
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, that's right.</font>

459
00:34:51,828 --> 00:34:54,130
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That's the number one thing
that you need to worry about.</font>

460
00:34:55,899 --> 00:34:56,733
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But you know,</font>

461
00:34:57,567 --> 00:35:00,270
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">it's very hard to act surprised
when I already know about it.</font>

462
00:35:01,271 --> 00:35:04,941
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Acting surprised at
the surprise party and the cake.</font>

463
00:35:05,809 --> 00:35:06,810
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">And the present, too.</font>

464
00:35:09,412 --> 00:35:10,313
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What?</font>

465
00:35:12,215 --> 00:35:14,951
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">There's probably no present.</font>

466
00:35:18,288 --> 00:35:19,823
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It wasn't my business, I know that,</font>

467
00:35:21,424 --> 00:35:24,394
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">but Nao searched desperately
for your present until today.</font>

468
00:35:26,730 --> 00:35:27,564
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I know that.</font>

469
00:35:32,602 --> 00:35:33,436
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I see.</font>

470
00:35:36,072 --> 00:35:37,006
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Of course.</font>

471
00:36:04,300 --> 00:36:05,201
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uehara.</font>

472
00:36:05,769 --> 00:36:07,971
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Is that Yoshikawa?</font>

473
00:36:08,905 --> 00:36:09,906
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What is she doing?</font>

474
00:36:12,375 --> 00:36:13,910
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yoshikawa, what's wrong?</font>

475
00:36:15,612 --> 00:36:16,446
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Is something wrong?</font>

476
00:36:19,115 --> 00:36:20,316
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uehara.</font>

477
00:36:20,950 --> 00:36:23,386
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Thank goodness.</font>

478
00:36:24,187 --> 00:36:25,488
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Thank goodness.</font>

479
00:36:25,922 --> 00:36:28,191
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I thought you might have been
in an accident or something.</font>

480
00:36:31,027 --> 00:36:31,861
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm sorry.</font>

481
00:36:32,796 --> 00:36:34,097
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I should have called you.</font>

482
00:36:45,041 --> 00:36:46,442
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uehara, you're hurt.</font>

483
00:36:47,911 --> 00:36:50,413
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">So there was an accident?</font>

484
00:36:51,214 --> 00:36:52,048
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Does it hurt?</font>

485
00:36:52,115 --> 00:36:53,583
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Shouldn't we go to a hospital?</font>

486
00:36:54,350 --> 00:36:55,385
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm fine.</font>

487
00:36:56,619 --> 00:36:59,322
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">More importantly, Natsume...</font>

488
00:37:02,158 --> 00:37:03,059
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Natsume?</font>

489
00:37:03,927 --> 00:37:06,262
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No. I'm fine now.</font>

490
00:37:07,997 --> 00:37:09,399
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It wasn't that bad to begin with.</font>

491
00:37:10,533 --> 00:37:11,367
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">See you.</font>

492
00:37:11,868 --> 00:37:14,003
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Wait a minute.</font>

493
00:37:14,938 --> 00:37:16,206
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Wait a minute.</font>

494
00:37:18,074 --> 00:37:19,309
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You're bleeding.</font>

495
00:37:20,643 --> 00:37:22,579
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You need to get it cleaned.</font>

496
00:37:24,781 --> 00:37:27,517
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-I'm really okay.
-You are not. You're a mess.</font>

497
00:37:27,584 --> 00:37:30,386
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-It would be best to do what she says.
-But you waited so long for...</font>

498
00:37:30,486 --> 00:37:31,321
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yes!</font>

499
00:37:31,654 --> 00:37:34,190
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Today is his birthday.
What were you doing?</font>

500
00:37:34,257 --> 00:37:36,059
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I made lots of plans and I was waiting...</font>

501
00:37:48,471 --> 00:37:50,607
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Did you hear all that?</font>

502
00:37:52,242 --> 00:37:53,376
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What?</font>

503
00:38:00,416 --> 00:38:04,254
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You remembered my birthday.</font>

504
00:38:05,922 --> 00:38:07,523
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm really happy!</font>

505
00:38:11,461 --> 00:38:12,295
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What?</font>

506
00:38:14,330 --> 00:38:15,198
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That's...</font>

507
00:38:18,201 --> 00:38:20,670
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">what I wrote on the schedule.</font>

508
00:38:34,851 --> 00:38:36,920
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Well, I will get changed.</font>

509
00:38:37,287 --> 00:38:38,454
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Look after Natsume.</font>

510
00:38:52,435 --> 00:38:53,603
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">How embarrassing.</font>

511
00:38:56,005 --> 00:38:58,441
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">He knew about it from the beginning.</font>

512
00:39:09,619 --> 00:39:11,354
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">She really overdid the decoration.</font>

513
00:39:33,776 --> 00:39:35,712
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">So the birthday party was a failure.</font>

514
00:39:40,216 --> 00:39:41,317
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That's right.</font>

515
00:39:41,617 --> 00:39:44,854
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I thought the two of us would be able
to celebrate together.</font>

516
00:40:02,338 --> 00:40:03,973
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Why were you fighting?</font>

517
00:40:08,311 --> 00:40:10,413
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Why? Well...</font>

518
00:40:12,281 --> 00:40:16,886
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I thought you were acting strangely
when I saw you today.</font>

519
00:40:19,188 --> 00:40:23,059
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I made some guys upset because of a girl.</font>

520
00:40:29,432 --> 00:40:31,768
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It seems like you don't believe me.</font>

521
00:40:34,203 --> 00:40:38,007
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Well, it's kind of strange.</font>

522
00:40:39,809 --> 00:40:40,643
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What is?</font>

523
00:40:42,678 --> 00:40:43,513
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">See?</font>

524
00:40:43,813 --> 00:40:45,014
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You're irritated.</font>

525
00:40:49,018 --> 00:40:49,852
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm not.</font>

526
00:40:52,121 --> 00:40:53,022
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm just my usual self.</font>

527
00:41:05,968 --> 00:41:06,803
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">There.</font>

528
00:41:06,869 --> 00:41:07,703
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">All done.</font>

529
00:41:13,609 --> 00:41:14,444
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Thanks.</font>

530
00:41:16,579 --> 00:41:17,847
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You're welcome.</font>

531
00:41:44,006 --> 00:41:45,675
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uehara, are you okay?</font>

532
00:41:46,109 --> 00:41:46,943
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yes.</font>

533
00:41:56,385 --> 00:41:57,320
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I will be off then.</font>

534
00:41:59,455 --> 00:42:01,057
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Natsume, eat with us.</font>

535
00:42:01,124 --> 00:42:02,525
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I couldn't do that.</font>

536
00:42:02,992 --> 00:42:04,360
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I can tell if I should stay or not.</font>

537
00:42:04,660 --> 00:42:05,828
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-See you.
-Natsume.</font>

538
00:42:18,407 --> 00:42:19,242
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Sorry.</font>

539
00:42:19,308 --> 00:42:21,210
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I was very late, wasn't I?</font>

540
00:42:23,112 --> 00:42:24,413
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Shall we eat?</font>

541
00:42:25,381 --> 00:42:26,749
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">There's so much food!</font>

542
00:42:30,419 --> 00:42:32,421
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Natsume's acting kind of strange.</font>

543
00:42:37,126 --> 00:42:37,960
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yes.</font>

544
00:42:39,395 --> 00:42:40,863
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I wonder if something happened to him.</font>

545
00:42:48,905 --> 00:42:49,739
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yoshikawa.</font>

546
00:42:52,041 --> 00:42:52,875
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Listen.</font>

547
00:42:53,075 --> 00:42:53,910
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's okay.</font>

548
00:42:55,878 --> 00:42:56,712
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Go.</font>

549
00:42:57,580 --> 00:42:58,414
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What?</font>

550
00:43:00,449 --> 00:43:04,153
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">After all, he's the first friend
you've ever had, Uehara.</font>

551
00:43:05,955 --> 00:43:08,090
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I told you, he's not my first.</font>

552
00:43:08,157 --> 00:43:10,693
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But wait a second.</font>

553
00:43:15,731 --> 00:43:16,632
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uehara.</font>

554
00:43:17,600 --> 00:43:18,801
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Happy birthday!</font>

555
00:43:22,738 --> 00:43:25,641
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm so glad that you were born,</font>

556
00:43:26,909 --> 00:43:31,547
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">and that I could meet you like this.</font>

557
00:43:39,388 --> 00:43:40,223
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">And...</font>

558
00:43:41,657 --> 00:43:45,461
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">About your present,</font>

559
00:43:48,231 --> 00:43:51,500
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I wasn't able to get it in time,
but I promise...</font>

560
00:43:55,338 --> 00:43:56,172
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I don't need one.</font>

561
00:43:58,474 --> 00:44:00,576
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You've given me so much already.</font>

562
00:44:09,252 --> 00:44:10,086
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Thank you.</font>

563
00:44:17,159 --> 00:44:17,994
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Sure.</font>

564
00:44:37,446 --> 00:44:38,281
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Natsume.</font>

565
00:44:43,019 --> 00:44:44,387
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I finally caught up with you.</font>

566
00:44:45,755 --> 00:44:47,657
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-What are you doing here?
-Walking you home.</font>

567
00:44:47,723 --> 00:44:48,557
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What?</font>

568
00:44:49,258 --> 00:44:50,092
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What about Nao?</font>

569
00:44:50,559 --> 00:44:51,394
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">She's waiting for me.</font>

570
00:44:52,728 --> 00:44:53,562
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You're impossible.</font>

571
00:44:54,797 --> 00:44:56,032
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You're doing the wrong thing.</font>

572
00:44:56,432 --> 00:44:57,366
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hurry up and go home.</font>

573
00:44:58,567 --> 00:45:00,002
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Stay with Nao.</font>

574
00:45:13,416 --> 00:45:14,250
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What?</font>

575
00:45:15,117 --> 00:45:16,752
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You have something you want to say, right?</font>

576
00:45:18,154 --> 00:45:19,188
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No, you do.</font>

577
00:45:19,955 --> 00:45:20,790
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What?</font>

578
00:45:23,559 --> 00:45:24,894
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You've been acting weird lately.</font>

579
00:45:26,996 --> 00:45:27,830
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You too?</font>

580
00:45:33,069 --> 00:45:37,340
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">During that fight,
you never hit back once.</font>

581
00:45:39,942 --> 00:45:40,776
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's not like you.</font>

582
00:45:44,780 --> 00:45:45,848
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What are you talking about?</font>

583
00:45:47,083 --> 00:45:48,718
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm not good at fighting like you are.</font>

584
00:45:53,255 --> 00:45:54,490
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Are you sick or something?</font>

585
00:45:55,524 --> 00:45:56,359
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What?</font>

586
00:45:57,026 --> 00:45:59,295
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Bad health leads to all sorts of problems.</font>

587
00:45:59,929 --> 00:46:01,230
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I've even fainted before.</font>

588
00:46:02,298 --> 00:46:04,767
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Anyway, you need to eat right.</font>

589
00:46:08,137 --> 00:46:08,971
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">This is ridiculous.</font>

590
00:46:09,805 --> 00:46:11,107
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Why are you laughing?</font>

591
00:46:13,843 --> 00:46:15,177
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">This is so ridiculous.</font>

592
00:46:21,917 --> 00:46:24,587
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What is it with you two?</font>

593
00:46:27,423 --> 00:46:28,324
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Natsume?</font>

594
00:46:29,191 --> 00:46:30,025
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yes.</font>

595
00:46:31,460 --> 00:46:32,495
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yes, it's true.</font>

596
00:46:34,430 --> 00:46:35,598
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's not like me.</font>

597
00:46:37,066 --> 00:46:38,401
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Even I think that, actually.</font>

598
00:46:39,802 --> 00:46:40,803
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm an idiot.</font>

599
00:46:48,878 --> 00:46:49,712
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">So...</font>

600
00:46:51,947 --> 00:46:53,883
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm going say something
unlike my usual self.</font>

601
00:46:57,052 --> 00:46:57,887
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What?</font>

602
00:47:01,490 --> 00:47:02,324
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What...</font>

603
00:47:09,398 --> 00:47:11,567
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What would you do
if I said that I liked Nao?</font>

604
00:47:43,299 --> 00:47:45,935
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">TO UEHARA</font>

605
00:49:32,541 --> 00:49:35,945
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">THIS DRAMA IS FICTIONAL.</font>

606
00:49:36,011 --> 00:49:38,013
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Subtitle translation by
Kumar Sivasubramanian</font>
